channel.title: Needing some help removing varrock fountain
channel.description:
Hey guys well i've recently decided that the varrock fountain is just a biggg object taking in alot of space so i've decided to remove it but i cannot seem to figure out how to do it.
If someone could help me with it it'd be awesome!
Using a Renamed client.

item.title: Needing some help removing varrock fountain
item.dc:creator: @Lin Lin
item.description:
@Lin wrote:

I already told you how to do this. You “create” an object with the ID of nothing where the fountain is. I don’t remember the exact ID, but an object list certainly has it. Since PI is based off of wL and probably uses the object “creating/deleting” code Federexer made way back in the day, it probably has a method to remove objects.
